Altitudinal range limits. Imagoes are found up to 1700m above sea level (
Okada 1938
). They may be transported by the wind to heights and biotope that are atypical for the species such as the snowfield of the Vilyuchinsky volcano which sits at 2100m above sea level ( Russia , Kamchatka, see material).
